version_description:
What’s New:

Fill & Sign is now available for iPhone, with all your favorite iPad features:
-Scan paper forms with your camera
-Open and fill files from email
-Tap to add text and checkmarks
-Easily create and apply your signature
-Save forms and send to others via email
-Fill forms faster with reusable text from your profile
